# Usage: pkgdiff newfile
#        pkgdiff oldfile newfile
#
# Will output a patch ready for the NetBSD Pkgs Collection (unified
# diff, plus no RCS IDs if possible). If only newfile is given,
# oldfile is assumed as newfile.orig.
#

